  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is:

      Evaluation of the safety and effectiveness of the Compression Anastomosis Ring (CAR™ 27)
      device for creation of circular, colorectal anastomoses in previously radiated patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
